test_list_of_zeros:
assert [7] == [0, 0, 0]
  At index 0 diff: 7 != 0
  Right contains 2 more items, first extra item: 0
  Full diff:
  - [0, 0, 0]
  + [7]
test_negate_of_lists:
assert [7] == [-7]
  At index 0 diff: 7 != -7
  Full diff:
  - [-7]
  ?  -
  + [7]
test_non_divisibles_1:
assert [7] == []
  Left contains one more item: 7
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [7]
  ?  +
